{"word":"στρόμβος","slug":"στρόμβος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>στρόμβος</b></el> <el>(στρόμβος, ὁ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:στρέφω'><el>στρέφω</el></a>\n<p/><i>a body rounded</i> or <i>spun round</i>: hence,<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a top</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>turbo</el>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>a whirlwind</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><i>a snail</i>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}